<i>noun</i>: 탈선 [탈썬], 일탈 [일탈], 외도 [외ː도/웨ː도] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탈선 [탈썬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. derailment</dd><br>
<dd>기차나 전차 등의 바퀴가 선로를 벗어남.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of the wheels of a train, streetcar, etc., jumping the rails.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deviation; going astray</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동 등이 나쁜 방향으로 빗나감.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one’s word, behavior, etc., turning to a bad direction.</dd><br>
<dd>3. divergence; digression</dd><br>
<dd>목적에서 벗어나 딴 길로 빠짐.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of starting to do something else, instead of seeking one’s own goal.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>일탈 [일탈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. deviation; departure</dd><br>
<dd>정해진 영역이나 체계, 또는 원래의 목적이나 방향에서 벗어남.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of getting out of a given sphere or system, or deviating from the original goal or direction.</dd><br>
<dd>2. deviation; breakaway; digression</dd><br>
<dd>도리나 사회의 규범에서 벗어남.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of going astray from one's duty or social norms.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>외도 [외ː도/웨ː도]</dt><br>
<dd>1. injustice</dd><br>
<dd>올바르지 않은 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act that is not right.</dd><br>
<dd>2. adultery; affair</dd><br>
<dd>배우자가 아닌 사람과 성관계를 가지는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of having sexual intercourse with a person who is not one's spouse.</dd><br>
<dd>3. excursion; deviation</dd><br>
<dd>본업이 아닌 다른 일을 시도함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of trying another job, not one's regular occupation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>